![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/17261d1d-6495-4475-a5a6-8e0cf5a511c6/15046.jpg?format=original)

Jey Uso opens RAW wondering if he cost himself the World Championship by helping Roman Reigns. But family is more important than anything to Jey Uso.

He's interrupted by LA Knight who is furious about losing the fatal four way. Before Knight and USO could come to blows, Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed come out to mock them.

Bron Breakker & Bronson Reed vs. Jey Uso & LA Knight is announced for tonight.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/adfd8a92-11b4-46ec-a6d3-f1ab1672800a/processed_15047.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e7867fd9-56d8-404d-9fa3-15eb82609810/15055.jpg?format=original)

*   **_KABUKI WARRIORS DEF. THE JUDGEMENT DAY_**
    

Asuka taps out Roxanne Perez to prove to Iyo Sky that the Kabuki Warriors can take care of Judgement Day

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e54b67a2-5c2b-4326-9760-1d7f1bb36e31/15052.jpg?format=original)

Stephanie Vaquer's opponent for the Women's World Championship is revealed to be Iyo Sky!!!

They will wrestle for the championship at WWE Wrestlepalooza

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/600b352b-acb6-4a0d-8a1f-f47e37de623e/15069.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_FINN BALOR DEF. DRAGON LEE_**
    

The Paris, France audience LOSES THEIR MINDS for Finn Balor as he gets a victory over Dragon Lee in a pretty good match

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6ea08e65-2f19-4a57-8514-f68d80d8336f/15082.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_PENTA AND THE WAR RAIDERS DEF THE NEW DAY_**
    

The New Day took this “fans” cell phone from the front row and destroyed it on the way down to the ring before they hold a Funeral for the Tag Team division during the commercial break.

Penta and the War Raiders win with the War Raiders botching their finish and Penta hitting a Mexican Destroyer

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f3ba6f22-73ea-433f-a715-3362af5e6433/15070.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/15d877f2-861d-495f-83bf-d7d5b110cdcf/15071.jpg?format=original)

Nikki Bella asks Iyo if she's ok alone with the Kabuki Warriors. Iyo says she is. Asuka gets possessive over Iyo saying Nikki is not a friend. Only Asuka and Kairi are.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a9b15454-a269-4b3e-8a1c-37bc933984a5/15094.jpg?format=original)

Rhea Ripley is interviewed backstage. She's asked about how it feels that Iyo is getting a title shot before her. Rhea said that she just has to keep working harder and she'll get her shot again.

She's cut off by Asuka and Kairi backstage. Asuka tells Asuka to stay away from Iyo. Rhea tells Asuka to stop pushing her buttons. Asuka says that she's been pushing for 10 years in WWE and she won't back down from anyone.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4972df6d-189d-4041-aa0b-da7c1cf78dfd/15080.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: Dominik Mysterio def. AJ Styles_**
    

El Grande Americano costs AJ Styles the Intercontinental Championship by hitting him with a loaded headbutt behind the ref's back.

Dominik Mysterio's weeks of planning and scheming with Americano paid off and now he's coming for the AAA Mega Championship

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dd2fcf36-63f3-4225-ba4e-12c1306faedb/15092.jpg?format=original)

Michael Cole announces that Roman Reigns has multiple broken ribs after the attack from Bron and Bronson. Roman will be out indefinitely.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a0cad305-cc8f-4c66-a85d-10c291434e8c/15093.jpg?format=original)

Rusev gives his respect to Sheamus for their fight last night. He suggests that now that Sheamus knows that Rusev is the better man that maybe they can be friends again. Rusev puts the rest of the roster on notice not to get in his way.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5e0a4f7b-545c-4739-b709-d81c78272084/processed_15087.jpg?format=original)

CM Punk calls out Seth Rollins and his music plays but it's Becky Lynch. Punk says he sees where this is going and wants no part of it.

Becky asks Punk if he thinks his actions only affect Seth Rollins?? They affected Becky Lynch and her family. When Punk left the WWE it was his name the fans chanted over both her and her husband's matches.

Becky says they need CM Punk to get out of the way because wrestling doesn't need him. He doesn't fit the Vision.

CM Punk says the Vision must be blurry because how is this a ten year beef over the fans chanting his name. Its not his fault he's the Best in the World.

Meanwhile CM Punk is working the house shows and he didn't see Becky or Seth anywhere. Rollins hides behind Bronson and Bron. And now he hides behind his wife.

CM Punk says this beef between him and Rollins will NEVER BE OVER. This finally brings out Rollins. Rollins, from the entrance ramp, says if Punk has something to say, say it to his face.

Becky doesn't let Punk. Rollins leaves. Becky slaps Punk across the face.

Punk says Becky Lynch is going to regret putting her hands on him. Becky says she already does. She has his nasty sweat on her hands.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0c0932a1-c268-4059-a2f0-75acf097d2ed/15091.jpg?format=original)

CM Punk tries to catch up to Seth Rollins, but Adam Pearce tells him they've already left. CM Punk asks where SmackDown is on Friday, Adam Pearce says Chicago.

Punk smiles HARD. He's got something planned.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f69f3697-b34a-4a72-8218-78b25308c278/15100.jpg?format=original)

# **_The Usos are reunited!!!_**

*   ## **_Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed def. Jey Uso and LA Knight_**
    

Post match the Brons destroyed Jey Uso and they would've done him in like Roman Reigns but Jimmy Uso comes to the save!!!